		<div class="lia-message-body lia-component-body" id="messagebodydisplay_0_1" class="lia-message-body">
	
		<div class="lia-message-body-content">
			
                
                    <BLOCKQUOTE><HR />Rock_Raider_fan_no1 wrote:<BR /><BLOCKQUOTE><HR />Samlooploop wrote:<BR /><BLOCKQUOTE><HR />Rock_Raider_fan_no1 wrote:<BR /><BLOCKQUOTE><HR />Haroldosaur wrote:<BR /><P>Chapter 8 Part 3:</P><P>&nbsp;</P><P>"A staff, of all weapons?" Plue queried. "Seems pretty uninteresting."</P><P>&nbsp;</P><P>"That's why I like it." Intrepid explained. "A staff is both unassuming and versatile..."</P><HR /></BLOCKQUOTE><P>You know, a staff could be modified to have energy or electrical output for a higher versatility. <img class="emoticon emoticon-thinking" id="thinking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/thinking.png" alt="Thinking" title="Thinking" /> Although, that addition may make it unassuming... <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /></P><HR /></BLOCKQUOTE><P>I want one that detaches into escrima sticks.<img class="emoticon emoticon-cool" id="cool" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/cool.png" alt="Cool" title="Cool" /></P><HR /></BLOCKQUOTE><P>What are those? <img class="emoticon emoticon-thinking" id="thinking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/thinking.png" alt="Thinking" title="Thinking" /> For some reason they remind me of the sticks that Tak uses to fight in TimeFlyz. <img class="emoticon emoticon-thinking" id="thinking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/thinking.png" alt="Thinking" title="Thinking" /></P><HR /></BLOCKQUOTE><P>They're pretty much just short sticks to hit people with. Nightwing uses them, if you're looking for an example.</P>
                
            
			
